Title: WTF# is Kit Eason?
Description: In this interview, we talk to Kit Eason, author of Stylish F#, F# from the Ground Up, etc. We cover his background, experience in education, side projects, and plans for future ventures! We also pose a listener challenge, due Feb 21, 2021.
